race.comment: UNDER ANESTHETIC (8) could manage only second at this track last time but turned heads when clocking a convincing 22.72 over 400m at The Gardens the start prior. Has the ability and expected to go close again. HANNAH GOANNA (3) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from five tries. Scored by 4.5 lengths last time (20.00) in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Can feature with the right run. WILGUNYA PRINCE (7) shapes well for this backing up a swift 20.00 win with success at this track over 350m last time, recording 19.99. Expecting another bold showing. WHERE'S THE BOSS (1) is a course and distance winner who cannot be left out of calculations.
